  "Description": {
    "English": "Advanced light metal alloy traded throughout the galactic Outer Edge. Often used in the interiors of trading shuttles to reduce weight as they ascend from planets with high gravitational fields.<br><br>Crafted from <span class=\"name name-special\">Aronium</span>, <span class=\"name name-special\">Magno-Gold</span> and <span class=\"name name-special\">Grantine</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "星系外缘各处均有交易的高级轻金属合金。通常用在贸易飞船的内部，减轻飞船从高重力的星球升空时的重量。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-special\">阿洛姆</span>、<span class=\"name name-special\">镍锰金</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">格兰丁</span>制作。",
    "TencentChinese": "星系外缘各处均有交易的高级轻金属合金。通常用在贸易飞船的内部，减轻飞船从高重力的星球升空时的重量。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-special\">阿洛姆</span>、<span class=\"name name-special\">镍锰金</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">格兰丁</span>制作。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "在外圍星域全境廣泛流通的先進輕合金。常用於貿易船的內部架構，以減輕重量，便於從高重力場星球起飛。<br><br>可使用<span class=\"name name-special\">鑨</span>、<span class=\"name name-special\">磁金</span>與<span class=\"name name-special\">大鋰</span>製造。"
  },
